title: Mad Season - Above + Live EP
description:
Mad Season - Above (1995)
Mad Season - Live (1995)
320kbps each

The Live EP was a freebie from Sam The Record Man (possibly other retailers as well).  It contains 4 tracks (5 songs) from Above, recorded live at the Moore Theatre in Seattle, WA.  That&#039;s the same show where the VHS was recorded.  Yes, VHS.  These are NOT from the VHS, these are ripped from the CD that was NOT made available commercially.

Hope you enjoy... I&#039;m DL&#039;ing the VHS rip right now, since my VHS is toast.

I love(d) these guys and they&#039;re a massive part of my musical experience.

Enjoy,
